{"tid":1861663,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【港共政府無新招】對付醫護罷工，會繼續用黑警同黑社會/網軍恐嚇","createTime":"2020-02-04T08:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T10:18:58.000Z","uid":205733,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"25ea3f0a46ca3bad12e53d1fd792a57bdbc4b004","tid":1861663,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">大家有眼見<br />\n對付和理shop : 黑警+黑社會+網軍恐嚇<br />\n對付和理塞 : 黑警+黑社會+網軍恐嚇<br />\n對付示威 : 黑警+黑社會+網軍恐嚇<br />\n對付連儂牆 : 黑警+黑社會+網軍恐嚇</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港共政權係無良知/無道德/無底綫既政府<br />\n所以對付罷工：都一定係 黑警+黑社會+網軍恐嚇 鐡三角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日醫護罷工，黑警企圖搞事唔係好跡象<br />\n即係代表其他港共打手會陸續出場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>醫護之後好有可能將會<br />\n- 收到恐嚇電話<br />\n- 搞你屋企人<br />\n- 罷工現場可能有人煽動暴力，製造機會現場濫捕<br />\n- 之後順理成章用暴力<br />\n- 甚至揾黑社會打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如何應對？：靠集體意志，工會壓力<br />\n工會要預先發出聲明：<br />\n若果上述事情出現係任何一個罷工既人士身上<br />\n將會無限期罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"70da76131c91fab9537deb1992a7bfca65dfaebe","tid":1861663,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:31:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"64cb0b3fd0a63581296cad775549aa0c735cd12c","tid":1861663,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"各醫護請有心理準備"},{"pid":"420e37e321a732603723d5bdda98c9a622d2c956","tid":1861663,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1